00:24:06,360 --> 00:24:08,120
Why?

250
00:24:15,600 --> 00:24:20,540
If you were going to fool me, then you should've fooled me to the end. What's the reason for revealing it now?

251
00:24:21,680 --> 00:24:24,780
Isn't it better if I didn't know?

252
00:24:27,740 --> 00:24:30,100
It's just a manic episode.

253
00:24:30,100 --> 00:24:33,020
It would have been okay like that.

254
00:24:35,880 --> 00:24:39,960
I couldn't deceive you any longer.

255
00:24:39,960 --> 00:24:41,740
Why?!

256
00:24:42,420 --> 00:24:45,880
Why couldn't you fool me? You deceived me just fine until now.

257
00:24:47,880 --> 00:24:49,660
 Was it fun?

258
00:24:50,920 --> 00:24:54,600
I who couldn't distinguish if it was you or a ghost.

259
00:24:54,600 --> 00:24:56,880
Was it fun watching me like that?

260
00:24:56,880 --> 00:25:01,260
No, it really wasn't like that.

261
00:25:06,980 --> 00:25:09,320
Agh!

262
00:25:13,780 --> 00:25:16,200
I'm going insane, Na Bong Seon.

263
00:25:18,420 --> 00:25:21,220
A ghost?

264
00:25:21,220 --> 00:25:24,900
Doesn't this only come out of summer special episodes?

265
00:25:25,980 --> 00:25:31,920
Then who did I like? Was it you or the ghost?

266
00:25:34,020 --> 00:25:36,860
Why did you do that? Why?

267
00:25:39,580 --> 00:25:41,700
Because I liked you.

268
00:25:44,640 --> 00:25:47,000
I liked you so much.

269
00:25:47,720 --> 00:25:51,680
From the first time I saw you, I liked you so much.

270
00:25:53,100 --> 00:25:56,700
I wanted to keep you next to me even like that.

271
00:26:12,400 --> 00:26:16,280
I think I'm going to need some time. Go in and rest.

272
00:27:11,010 --> 00:27:14,670
Hey, Seon Woo! What are you doing here at this hour?

273
00:27:14,670 --> 00:27:15,860
I'll just sleep here and go.

274
00:27:15,860 --> 00:27:19,600
Hey, hey, hey, hey. What is it?

275
00:27:19,600 --> 00:27:23,120
Are things not good with that Bong Sook girl? Did you break up?

276
00:27:23,120 --> 00:27:28,140
No, it's not that. I'm going to rest.

277
00:27:32,640 --> 00:27:34,840
What is it?

278
00:27:35,920 --> 00:27:39,580
He has so much charisma.

279
00:27:39,580 --> 00:27:43,460
I think my son can be kind of cool when he's like that.

280
00:28:02,240 --> 00:28:06,220
No, no, no. This isn't the time to be like this.

281
00:28:08,900 --> 00:28:10,980
I can do this, Shin Soon Ae!

282
00:28:12,580 --> 00:28:15,250
First look into Officer Choi.

283
00:28:15,250 --> 00:28:17,960
Then tell Na Bong Seon.

284
00:28:17,960 --> 00:28:19,750
Do it!

285
00:30:09,240 --> 00:30:13,140
Now where did she go? I have to tell her about Officer Choi.

286
00:30:13,140 --> 00:30:15,400
Her bag is gone, too.

287
00:30:16,680 --> 00:30:18,560
By chance,

288
00:30:19,800 --> 00:30:22,690
did Na Bong Seon leave?

289
00:30:22,690 --> 00:30:24,600
No way.

290
00:30:24,600 --> 00:30:28,020
Oh, I'm going to go nuts.

291
00:30:30,280 --> 00:30:33,120
Hey, Joon! Where is the shredded crab meat?

292
00:30:33,120 --> 00:30:35,820
I think Bong put it in the refrigerator. It's not there?

293
00:30:35,820 --> 00:30:39,480
Hey, hey, hey, hey. Call She-Bong.

294
00:30:39,480 --> 00:30:41,700
This is just wrong even as a summer cosplay.

295
00:30:41,700 --> 00:30:43,700
Isn't being late twice in a row too much?

296
00:30:43,700 --> 00:30:46,860
My goodness, her phone is turned off.

297
00:30:46,860 --> 00:30:49,560
Could it be that she's quitting because she had a huge fight with Chef yesterday?

298
00:30:49,560 --> 00:30:54,440
It's probably not that. She's not irresponsible.

299
00:30:54,440 --> 00:30:55,530
Oh, Chef!

300
00:30:55,530 --> 00:30:58,330
Why are you coming from that way today?

301
00:30:58,330 --> 00:31:00,050
-I'll go change my clothes.
-Chef.

302
00:31:00,050 --> 00:31:02,550
I'm not sure if you know this,

303
00:31:02,550 --> 00:31:05,070
but Bong Seon hasn't come to work yet.

304
00:31:05,070 --> 00:31:09,570
-Na Bong Seon?
-I was worried, so I called and her phone is off.

305
00:31:09,570 --> 00:31:11,770
She's not someone who is like that.

306
00:31:12,930 --> 00:31:14,890
I see. So get to work.

307
00:31:14,890 --> 00:31:18,900
Today's special is abalone pasta, right? Take it out and prep it.

308
00:31:18,900 --> 00:31:20,650
Yes, Chef.

309
00:32:41,860 --> 00:32:44,350
What are you saying that Bong Seon left?

310
00:32:44,350 --> 00:32:50,030
It appears that way. We thought she was just going to be late all day.

311
00:32:50,030 --> 00:32:53,210
But she even cleared out her locker.

312
00:32:53,210 --> 00:32:59,050
Actually, yesterday the mood didn't seem good with the Chef. I wonder if that's why.

313
00:32:59,050 --> 00:33:00,910
I can't believe it. But still,

314
00:33:00,910 --> 00:33:03,530
This is why workplace romances aren't good.

315
00:33:03,530 --> 00:33:07,910
If something happens between the two of them, one of them has to quit. Why?

316
00:33:07,910 --> 00:33:10,150
It will be extremely uncomfortable!

317
00:33:10,150 --> 00:33:13,590
 But still, I don't think this is the way.

318
00:33:13,590 --> 00:33:19,790
 There's really no time to be bored in this workplace. Shocking things are all lined up.

319
00:33:24,470 --> 00:33:27,570
Na Bong Seon has left.

320
00:33:28,750 --> 00:33:32,550
Then it means she didn't go back into that body.

321
00:33:33,370 --> 00:33:37,230
Shin Soon Ae, where are you? You ghost.

322
00:33:43,490 --> 00:33:47,970
 She opened her eyes. Father, she must be alive now.

323
00:33:47,970 --> 00:33:51,490
Are you okay, Bong Seon? Are you alert now?

324
00:33:53,320 --> 00:33:56,170
How did I end up here?

325
00:33:56,170 --> 00:33:59,950
I found you collapsed while I was on my way for morning exercise.

326
00:33:59,950 --> 00:34:05,370
I was going to report you to 911, but it didn't seem like you were unconscious.

327
00:34:05,370 --> 00:34:10,870
Do you know how scared I was when I received Father's call? My legs were trembling while carrying you on my back.

328
00:34:10,870 --> 00:34:15,110
You're anemic, aren't you? It's obvious you are by your pale face.

329
00:34:15,110 --> 00:34:17,930
I'm sorry for being such a nuisance.

330
00:34:17,930 --> 00:34:21,810
My goodness! Where are you going to go feeling like that?

331
00:34:21,810 --> 00:34:28,270
Seeing your bag, it looks like you left your work, too. Am I wrong?

332
00:34:29,390 --> 00:34:33,730
Regain your strength before you go. We're fine with that.

333
00:34:33,730 --> 00:34:36,730
No, no. I can go to my grandmother.

334
00:34:36,730 --> 00:34:39,570
Would your grandmother be happy to see you like this?

335
00:34:40,590 --> 00:34:45,550
I mean, even if you go, I'm saying to go when you feel better.

336
00:34:45,550 --> 00:34:48,450
The little thing doesn't listen.

337
00:34:48,450 --> 00:34:51,330
What are you going to do if you collapse again?

338
00:34:51,330 --> 00:34:56,450
Yeah, just do as we say. We owe you for everything you've done, too.

339
00:34:56,450 --> 00:35:02,330
This is the room my daughter used to use. You can stay because it's empty anyway.

340
00:35:03,750 --> 00:35:05,930
Let's leave, so she can rest comfortably.

341
00:35:05,930 --> 00:35:07,890
Why? I want to stay by her a little longer.

342
00:35:07,890 --> 00:35:11,350
Get out, kid. Rest comfortably.

343
00:35:11,350 --> 00:35:13,050
Yes.

344
00:35:13,050 --> 00:35:14,950
Hurry up and leave.

345
00:36:03,470 --> 00:36:07,050
Father, why are you so busy starting so early this morning?

346
00:36:07,850 --> 00:36:09,970
Have you been well?

347
00:36:10,950 --> 00:36:14,530
I'm really having a hard time, Father.

348
00:36:14,530 --> 00:36:20,910
It's hard because of Officer Choi and also because of Na Bong Seon.

349
00:36:20,910 --> 00:36:23,690
I wasn't planning to be this way.

350
00:36:25,490 --> 00:36:33,030
But why the porridge? Is Kyung Mo sick? Did he drink all night again?

351
00:36:33,030 --> 00:36:35,850
Ah, this kid.

352
00:36:35,850 --> 00:36:40,050
You have to cut off his spending money, if you want to fix his habit.

353
00:36:40,050 --> 00:36:43,130
Why? Is Kyung Mo lying down in my room?

354
00:36:43,130 --> 00:36:45,130
Yes.

355
00:36:52,630 --> 00:36:57,610
Why are you so startled? As if you've seen a ghost.

356
00:36:57,610 --> 00:36:58,990
I'm not.

357
00:36:58,990 --> 00:37:00,350
How are you here?

358
00:37:00,350 --> 00:37:04,390
I made some egg porridge. Even if you don't have an appetite, you have to eat it to get some energy.

359
00:37:04,390 --> 00:37:07,370
-Eat it.
-Thank you.

360
00:37:11,870 --> 00:37:14,130
I'll eat it well, Ahjussi.

361
00:37:14,130 --> 00:37:17,070
Okay, eat up.

362
00:37:21,270 --> 00:37:25,110
My father is really caring.

363
00:37:25,110 --> 00:37:27,110
But what happened?

364
00:37:27,110 --> 00:37:31,550
I was worried when I went to the storage room and you weren't there.

365
00:37:31,550 --> 00:37:37,610
It turned out like this. I had a dizzy spell and collapsed, but Ahjussi saw me.

366
00:37:37,610 --> 00:37:39,690
That's a good thing.

367
00:37:40,510 --> 00:37:46,450
Is it because of me, that you left Sun?

368
00:37:50,630 --> 00:37:55,590
I'm sorry. I didn't think it would turn out like this.

369
00:37:55,590 --> 00:38:03,210
Actually, I did resent you briefly. But when I thought about it, it was half my fault, too.

370
00:38:05,070 --> 00:38:09,730
But I made good memories with Chef, too. Why was that?

371
00:38:09,730 --> 00:38:14,150
It's someone I couldn't even look at before.

372
00:38:14,150 --> 00:38:18,130
You're making me feel sorry. You're too nice.

373
00:38:20,570 --> 00:38:24,710
But this isn't the time to feel sorry and do this.

374
00:38:24,710 --> 00:38:27,370
There's a more urgent situation that came up.

375
00:38:27,370 --> 00:38:28,570
What is it?

376
00:38:28,570 --> 00:38:33,050
When you were almost hit by the car that time, it was Officer Choi's doing.

377
00:38:33,050 --> 00:38:37,890
Officer Choi? Why would Officer Choi do that?

378
00:38:37,890 --> 00:38:41,350
I don't know either. We have to find out starting now.

379
00:38:41,350 --> 00:38:47,910
It isn't good to be seen by Officer Choi, so if possible don't come out. I'll be back after checking things out.

380
00:38:47,910 --> 00:38:49,930
Oh.

381
00:38:52,130 --> 00:38:54,550
-Na Bong Seon.
-Huh?

382
00:38:54,550 --> 00:38:59,650
My grudge might not be because I died a virgin.

383
00:39:10,930 --> 00:39:15,490
Officer Choi, why?

384
00:39:15,490 --> 00:39:19,330
-This is the last order! Cheer up even if it's hot!
-Yes, Chef!

385
00:39:19,330 --> 00:39:23,870
Table 4, salmon salad and 2 Shrek. Table 6, tenderloin steak and a Shrek.

386
00:39:23,870 --> 00:39:26,570
Table 7, mixed vegetables and 2 bean pasta.

387
00:39:26,570 --> 00:39:28,850
I'll do the vegetables. Min Soo, do the Shrek.

388
00:39:28,850 --> 00:39:29,690
-Joon!
-Yes?

389
00:39:29,690 --> 00:39:30,970
-You do the steak.
-Yes, Chef.

390
00:39:30,970 --> 00:39:32,390
Dong Cheol, take care of the salad.

391
00:39:32,390 --> 00:39:34,450
Ji Woong, cover Min Soo.

392
00:39:34,450 --> 00:39:36,890
-It's out!
-Yes, Chef!

393
00:39:36,890 --> 00:39:38,010
-Hey, Cordon.
-Yes.

394
00:39:38,010 --> 00:39:40,630
-Don't do the steak and help me with the arrangement.
-Yes.

395
00:39:40,630 --> 00:39:42,070
Where did the lentil beans go?

396
00:39:42,070 --> 00:39:44,630
Joon. Did you use up all the lentil beans I took out?

397
00:39:44,630 --> 00:39:45,890
Yes, should I go get it?

398
00:39:45,890 --> 00:39:47,990
Do what you were doing. I'll go.

399
00:39:47,990 --> 00:39:49,230
-Ji Woong.
-Yes, Chef?

400
00:39:49,230 --> 00:39:54,470
Give the customer at Table 7 more bread. He's been sucking his fingers since earlier.

401
00:39:59,010 --> 00:40:03,550
It doesn't appear to affect Chef at all that Bong left like that.

402
00:40:03,550 --> 00:40:07,390
He looks like he has more charisma than usual and he's in a good mood.

403
00:40:07,390 --> 00:40:13,050
I have these feelings for our Bong-Bong now, and I feel a little betrayed.

404
00:40:13,050 --> 00:40:16,270
I'm really disappointed in you, Chef.

405
00:40:16,270 --> 00:40:22,650
The way I see it, it isn't that the Chef is totally okay. There is this feeling that I'm feeling.

406
00:40:22,650 --> 00:40:24,750
What are you talking about?

407
00:40:24,750 --> 00:40:27,270
I've known Chef for a long time.

408
00:40:27,270 --> 00:40:32,590
He has this habit of acting like nothing is wrong the bigger the disappointment.

409
00:40:32,590 --> 00:40:36,430
His gaze was like that earlier, it was sad.

410
00:41:10,870 --> 00:41:13,390
Give it here!

411
00:41:13,390 --> 00:41:16,190
Are you going to ask for a leave again after carrying this?

412
00:41:16,190 --> 00:41:21,070
Now it feels more real, getting abused by you. Give it to me. I can do it.

413
00:41:21,070 --> 00:41:23,430
Like I don't know you.

414
00:41:23,430 --> 00:41:25,790
Just look at that.

415
00:41:25,790 --> 00:41:28,870
How does she expect to be an officer being that weak?

416
00:41:28,870 --> 00:41:31,290
How can we send you out anywhere, it will worry us.

417
00:41:31,290 --> 00:41:35,230
But she said she always wanted to be a police officer, because she was weak since childhood.

418
00:41:35,230 --> 00:41:38,910
She's gotten much healthier now. She was always pale because of her anemia.

419
00:41:38,910 --> 00:41:42,130
She can't walk right.

420
00:41:42,130 --> 00:41:44,450
 Check out Officer Choi.

421
00:41:44,450 --> 00:41:49,550
 If he's an evil spirit, he might be able to see you, so be extremely careful.

422
00:41:54,450 --> 00:41:56,130
Work hard.

423
00:41:56,130 --> 00:42:00,890
Ow, my legs.

424
00:42:03,830 --> 00:42:07,710
Oh, she's weak. She's weak.

425
00:42:07,710 --> 00:42:11,970
Then it makes me want to possess you.

426
00:42:31,190 --> 00:42:32,590
 Officer Choi.

427
00:42:32,590 --> 00:42:35,330
 -Do you have the cutter?
-Yes.

428
00:42:35,330 --> 00:42:38,510
Give it here.

429
00:42:43,810 --> 00:42:44,690
 Here.

430
00:42:44,690 --> 00:42:46,830
 Oh, my diary.

431
00:42:53,630 --> 00:42:56,950
Your diary was in the policeman's desk drawer?

432
00:42:56,950 --> 00:43:01,230
Yeah, that drawer is the only one that is locked. It was strange starting then.

433
00:43:01,230 --> 00:43:03,870
When I was going to take my diary, he insisted on keeping it.

434
00:43:03,870 --> 00:43:08,230
If that's the case, then there is something in that diary that catches at him.

435
00:43:08,230 --> 00:43:11,250
I know. What could it be?

436
00:43:11,990 --> 00:43:14,590
It's your diary!

437
00:43:14,590 --> 00:43:19,870
-That's right. 
-Think about it carefully. Isn't there anything you remember?

438
00:43:36,390 --> 00:43:38,730
I don't know.

439
00:43:39,750 --> 00:43:47,650
Having a hard time in the water and the sound of strange music. Those keep going through my head.

440
00:43:47,650 --> 00:43:50,850
Okay. No need to push it.

441
00:43:50,850 --> 00:43:55,510
First, get that diary out. That seems most urgent.

442
00:43:56,510 --> 00:43:58,570
How do I get it out?

443
00:43:59,350 --> 00:44:04,610
This amounts to a chick's pee. It's so hot out.

444
00:44:04,610 --> 00:44:07,430
You're hot? Do you want me to cool you off?

445
00:44:08,170 --> 00:44:13,670
Do you like if I do that?

446
00:44:19,010 --> 00:44:21,050
 Chef!

447
00:44:21,050 --> 00:44:22,750
You worked hard. See you tomorrow.

448
00:44:22,750 --> 00:44:27,290
Chef, the hottest day is over, so if we eat some ginseng chicken and

449
00:44:27,290 --> 00:44:29,530
have some bottles of ginseng liquor,

450
00:44:29,530 --> 00:44:35,670
I feel like our lowered strength would start going up and flying high.

451
00:44:35,670 --> 00:44:38,630
Did the hottest day already pass?

452
00:44:38,630 --> 00:44:41,890
I'm not hungry, so you guys go eat.

453
00:44:41,890 --> 00:44:44,500
It's no fun because we eat together all the time.

454
00:44:44,500 --> 00:44:48,890
Okay, Chef. If you don't want chicken, then maybe beer.

455
00:44:48,890 --> 00:44:53,290
Oh, what am I to do? I really want to drink with Chef today!

456
00:44:53,290 --> 00:44:56,150
Let's go, Chef. I won't run away today.

457
00:44:56,150 --> 00:45:00,100
Ooooh!

458
00:45:00,100 --> 00:45:03,110
Kang Seon Woo! Kang Seon Woo!

459
00:45:03,110 --> 00:45:05,390
Kang Seon Woo!

460
00:45:07,070 --> 00:45:09,570
Drink up!

461
00:45:09,570 --> 00:45:11,090
Is there more to life than this?

462
00:45:11,090 --> 00:45:17,030
Sweating at work, then drinking beer and eating good food with our beloved family will do!

463
00:45:17,030 --> 00:45:20,910
How nice is it to be with the guys? Women are all a headache.

464
00:45:20,910 --> 00:45:28,190
Of course. There's a saying like this in Italy, everyone.

465
00:45:28,190 --> 00:45:30,130
Handle a bull from the front.

466
00:45:30,130 --> 00:45:35,870
When handling a horse, do it from the back. But when dealing with women, be careful of all directions!

467
00:45:35,870 --> 00:45:37,470
There's a saying like this!

468
00:45:37,470 --> 00:45:40,630
Beep Beep! Is that a saying from Jeolla-do?

469
00:45:40,630 --> 00:45:46,130
Seriously. Anyway, the point is women are all useless. They're wicked!

470
00:45:46,130 --> 00:45:49,570
There's no need for them. We don't need any of them!

471
00:45:50,410 --> 00:45:52,610
You startled me.

472
00:45:52,610 --> 00:45:55,370
It's decided, it's decided. It's been decided.

473
00:45:55,370 --> 00:45:58,950
From now on, whomever betrays us and dates a woman,

474
00:45:58,950 --> 00:46:03,690
I will remove all the good things for you.

475
00:46:05,930 --> 00:46:07,510
Go on in.

476
00:46:07,990 --> 00:46:11,810
-Chef.
-What?

477
00:46:11,810 --> 00:46:15,410
About Bong Seon. You're not going to give up like this, are you?

478
00:46:15,410 --> 00:46:20,530
-What?
-She's quite nice and good natured.

479
00:46:20,530 --> 00:46:24,090
The Bong that I know, from the time she first came to us,

480
00:46:24,090 --> 00:46:26,450
only had eyes for you, Chef.

481
00:46:26,450 --> 00:46:32,790
When she's washing dishes, serving, even on her break,

482
00:46:32,790 --> 00:46:35,310
her eyes only followed you, Chef.

483
00:46:35,310 --> 00:46:39,790
I respect you, Chef, but if you give up on Bong like this,

484
00:46:39,790 --> 00:46:42,590
I'll be disappointed in you.

485
00:46:42,590 --> 00:46:45,620
I know it's not my place to say this,

486
00:46:45,620 --> 00:46:50,630
but I want the two people that I like to be happy.

487
00:47:10,170 --> 00:47:14,090
What is it, Kang Soo Kyeong? You haven't gone yet? You shouldn't overdo it on your first day back.

488
00:47:14,090 --> 00:47:16,570
Yes, I'm going to leave soon.

489
00:47:16,570 --> 00:47:19,850
I ate dinner a little too early.

490
00:47:19,850 --> 00:47:23,890
This punk just eats and pees and eats and pees. Do some work!

