568
00:54:53,050 --> 00:54:55,330
You stupid girl.

569
00:54:55,330 --> 00:54:58,590
If you left me to go to him, you should at least be happy.

570
00:54:58,590 --> 00:55:02,970
You got dumped like a fool, quit your job, and you're not even eating.

