00:56:43,690 --> 00:56:45,930
You are very courteous. Have a seat.

586
00:56:45,930 --> 00:56:46,990
It's okay.

587
00:56:46,990 --> 00:56:50,250
Aigoo, just sit down.

588
00:56:50,250 --> 00:56:52,850
Is it because our place is shabby? Sit down.

589
00:56:52,850 --> 00:56:54,790
Yes.

590
00:57:02,390 --> 00:57:08,790
Ah, well. Bong Seon is living well.

591
00:57:08,790 --> 00:57:12,810
She's naturally sincere and a deep person.

592
00:57:12,810 --> 00:57:17,550
Aigoo, I'm not worried about her.

