01:00:37,490 --> 01:00:42,330
You're asking me what I'm talking about? Are you asking me because you don't know, you bastard?

613
01:00:42,330 --> 01:00:47,150
Why did you do that to Na  Bong Seon? Why did you hurt this weak and frail kid?!

614
01:00:47,150 --> 01:00:53,310
I've never seen someone as bright as her other than my sister.

615
01:00:53,310 --> 01:00:58,970
